dmca.title: Software Maker Wants Google To Remove Links To Alleged Circumvention Devices
dmca.body:
June 18, 2004

Oak Vale Networks, Inc.
[private]
Berkeley, CA 94705

Google, Inc.
Attn: Customer Support, DMCA Complaints
[private]
Mountain View, CA 94043

Re: Copyright Infringement Notification

I am writing to notify you of the presence of materials in the Google search engine which infringe upon copyrights owned by Oak Vale Networks, Inc.

The copyrighted work at issue is our company's "XenoCode" software product. The infringing material is included in the Google search results on the query "XenoCode crack" and "XenoCode cracks". The pertinent web sites and URLs are listed below:

www.freeserials.com - www.freserials.com/serials/view.php?dir=X&page=3
mscracks.com
